com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Enum LoggerProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LoggerProvider>
      • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.LoggerProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable< LoggerProvider> 

    public enum LoggerProvider
extends java.lang.Enum<LoggerProvider>
    Provides access to different JxBrowser Loggers which are used to log Browser, IPC and Chromium process messages.
    提供对用于记录浏览器，IPC和Chromium进程消息的不同JxBrowser Logger的访问。

      • getBrowserLogger

        public static java.util.logging.Logger getBrowserLogger()
        Returns Browser Logger which is used to log browser info, debug and error messages.

        You can use the return value to configure logging. For example, you can configure logging level or register your own Logger handlers.
        返回浏览器记录器，该记录器用于记录浏览器信息，调试和错误消息。您可以使用返回值来配置日志记录。例如，您可以配置日志记录级别或注册自己的Logger处理程序。
        Returns:
        a Browser Logger object. 浏览器记录器对象。

        public static java.util.logging.Logger getIPCLogger()

      • setLevel

        public static void setLevel(java.util.logging.Level newLevel)
        Sets the log level specifying which message levels will be logged by all JxBrowser loggers. Message levels lower than this value will be discarded. The level value Level.OFF can be used to turn off logging.
        设置日志级别，指定所有JxBrowser记录器将记录哪些消息级别。低于此值的消息级别将被丢弃。级别值Level.OFF可用于关闭日志记录。
        Parameters:
        newLevel - the new value for the log level (may be null). -日志级别的新值（可能是）。
